{"type": "article", "id": 6007, "title": "Tone 书架", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-09T07:32:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233940MaRG9N0dTFqiUvfB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t在日本东京武藏野艺术大学（Musashino Art University）的毕业展览上，该校设计专业毕业生 Mizuki Odashiro 的作品是一款名为「Tone」的书架，用简单的金属框架搭配令人惊艳的薄薄的彩色纱质面料，虽然看上去又轻又薄，但每一层却能够承受约 5 公斤的重量。整体采用 3m™ dual lock™ 粘扣进行组装与固定，结实稳固，薄纱料的安装业非常简单。整个书架的尺寸为 180 x 104 x 40 厘米。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233938yvVfR1Y27qsgJE6K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052339386NGfl7UnHuxRsXE3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233939Ripv1xbKLwSgVMsa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233939W4DkdpsxQl1C0MOP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}